{"type":null,"faqId":11622,"title":"G630-U00  WLAN待机的时候会自动断开，怎么解决，手机默认是什么设置？","answer":"<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">这个问题是休眠策略的问题。进入的方法：在主屏幕，点击</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\"> </span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">设置</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\"> &gt; </span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">无线和网络</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\"> &gt; WLAN</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">，再点击菜单键并进入高级</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\"> &gt; </span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">在休眠状态下保持</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:&quot;\">WLAN</span><span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\">连接，设置为“始终”。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\"><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\"><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&amp;imageId=32986\" alt=\"\" /><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\"><br />\n</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size:10.5pt;font-family:宋体;\"> </span>\n</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">注：手机默认设置是始终，也就是一直可以正常连接。如果调整休眠策略就会使得在待机时自动断开。</span><span>3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">个选项的含义如下：</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">始终</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：一直保持</span><span>WLAN</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的连接。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">仅限充电时</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">：只有在充电时才一直保持连接，如果不充电，待机后</span><span>3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟断开连接。</span> \n</p>\n<p>\n\t<b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">从不</span></b><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">（会增加数据网络流量）：待机后</span><span>3</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">分钟断开连接。</span> \n</p>\n<br />\n<p>\n\t<br />\n</p>","faqTypeId":143,